<span class="nt">&lt;h2</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">"11-각주-footnotes"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>11. 각주 (Footnotes)<span class="nt">&lt;/h2&gt;</span>

<span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>각주를 사용한 문장<span class="nt">&lt;sup</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">"fnref:1"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;a</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">"#fn:1"</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"footnote"</span> <span class="na">rel=</span><span class="s">"footnote"</span> <span class="na">role=</span><span class="s">"doc-noteref"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>1<span class="nt">&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;</span>
다른 각주를 사용한 문장<span class="nt">&lt;sup</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">"fnref:2"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;a</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">"#fn:2"</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"footnote"</span> <span class="na">rel=</span><span class="s">"footnote"</span> <span class="na">role=</span><span class="s">"doc-noteref"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>2<span class="nt">&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span>

<span class="nt">&lt;h2</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">"12-정의-목록-definition-lists"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>12. 정의 목록 (Definition Lists)<span class="nt">&lt;/h2&gt;</span>

<span class="nt">&lt;dl&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;dt&gt;</span>Jekyll<span class="nt">&lt;/dt&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;dd&gt;</span>정적 웹사이트 생성기<span class="nt">&lt;/dd&gt;</span>
