<span class="nt">&lt;/dl&gt;</span>

<span class="nt">&lt;h2</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">"13-이모지-emoji"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>13. 이모지 (Emoji)<span class="nt">&lt;/h2&gt;</span>

<span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>마크다운에서 이모지도 지원됩니다! :smile: :heart: :+1:<span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>

<span class="nt">&lt;h2</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">"14-html-직접-사용"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>14. HTML 직접 사용<span class="nt">&lt;/h2&gt;</span>

<span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>마크다운에서는 <span class="nt">&lt;kbd&gt;</span>Ctrl<span class="nt">&lt;/kbd&gt;</span> + <span class="nt">&lt;kbd&gt;</span>C<span class="nt">&lt;/kbd&gt;</span>처럼 HTML도 직접 사용할 수 있습니다.<span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>

<span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">style=</span><span class="s">"padding: 20px; background-color: #f0f0f0; border-radius: 5px;"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
  HTML로 스타일이 적용된 div 박스입니다.
<span class="nt">&lt;/div&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"footnotes"</span> <span class="na">role=</span><span class="s">"doc-endnotes"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
